    "Pieter Aaldring\n\nI have experiences Barbara the last couple of years during various TEN-T meetings in Brussels as a dedicated and professional international colleague. Her judgement on the chances of EU funding for various projects is beyond any doubt; she is critical but at the same time enthousiastic!"
